!! Collapsible

To make a collapsible element with [[Css]], just transition the `max-height` property

```css
.content {
	max-height: 100vh; /* should be big enough to fit content */
	overflow: hidden;
	transition: max-height 1s linear;
}

/* Example */
.content.collapsed {
	max-height: 0;
}
```
